description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 22, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 110, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Box for East, Leverage for South, and Nine Lives for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70225-84694-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [110 Votes, Common]
